{"tid":565901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲少女疑跑馬路　遭新巴撞傷危殆","createTime":"2018-02-19T12:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T14:41:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"0d11ec3adba0ebe6bc6ac71e0ed24f75c437d276","tid":565901,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:13:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180219/large/1519039823_16d2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180219%2Flarge%2F1519039823_16d2.jpg&h=51e5f2cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴灣昨晚發生嚴重交通意外！昨晚11時許，一輛新巴沿常安街東行，至常平街交界附近時，撞倒一名正橫過馬路的22歲少女。<br />\n<br />\n少女頭部重創，昏迷不醒，由救護員送院治理，經搶救後情況危殆。據現場消息指，當時少女正在常安街附近跑步，懷疑被駛經的巴士撞倒而受傷。"},{"pid":"de95051c8d1b7a9ce40e458e8cf6e40d893966b1","tid":565901,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"係咪掛著玩手機?"},{"pid":"5689ed2afbd853890d46c94e22d72320e7de5955","tid":565901,"uid":104591,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:24:17.000Z","msg":"累死個司機"},{"pid":"0b07b93b9f3142c4ee02dd83d220ba97d25a17df","tid":565901,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:32:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29612809f47cd7b27c49585fa26df2030f7019c7","tid":565901,"uid":91897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:34:12.000Z","msg":"呢到如果跑路邊好難會撞到"},{"pid":"787dc39e2734e904581a3afbac62e795d7c823c5","tid":565901,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"跑步唔好跑馬路呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算你守規則過, 唔代表d 車都守規則過"},{"pid":"c294dcb99eaf9f1d23cdc2a0a887ce85db0bbbc1","tid":565901,"uid":108467,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T14:41:39.000Z","msg":"踩單車都仲講得通<br />\n有乜理由喺馬路跑步㗎<br />\n<br />\n不過都希望佢大步𨈇過"}]}